data.description: Welcome home to 203 Birch Drive located in Midcity Lafayette surrounded by good food, fun and convenience.  Walk into the living room with recessed lighting, wood tile, cypress wet bar,a beautiful brick fireplace and cypress bookshelf built-ins. This home comes complete with a bonus room, closed floor plan, guest bathroom in the living area and a swimming pool with deck and fence.  The kitchen features a large dry island, stainless steel appliances, a breakfast nook and floor to ceiling custom cabinets with ample storage.  Enjoy entertaining under your covered patio in the rain, or in the pool while soaking up some sunshine! Attain the 15'x20' storage shed on cement slab; roll up door; and spray foam insulated for all your packing and storing needs.  Schedule your tour today!
